# ğŸ™ï¸ Real-Time Speech Transcription & Translation

![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8+-blue.svg)
![Transformers](https://img.shields.io/badge/HuggingFace-Transformers-yellow.svg)

**Real-Time Speech Transcription & Translation** is a powerful application that captures audio from your system in real-time, transcribes speech using OpenAI's **Whisper large-v3-turbo**, and translates it into multiple languages. This project is optimized for **low latency** and supports **CUDA acceleration** for fast processing on GPUs.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

âœ”ï¸ **Real-time transcription** from any audio source using **PyAudio loopback**.  
âœ”ï¸ **Multi-language support** â€“ transcribes and translates speech into **English, Spanish, French, and German**.  
âœ”ï¸ **Noise reduction** with `noisereduce` to improve transcription accuracy.  
âœ”ï¸ **Optimized for speed** â€“ utilizes **CUDA (GPU)** acceleration for fast inference.  
âœ”ï¸ **Typing animation** in the GUI for a more dynamic experience.  
âœ”ï¸ **Live word counter** to track real-time transcription.  
âœ”ï¸ **Clear and structured UI** using **Tkinter** with easy start/stop controls.  

